fields.name: Car wash Sponge
fields.description: Nothing beats washing your car with the classic Car Wash Sponge. This sponge delivers excellent value for money, and it is so soft that it won't damage the car's body paintwork.y

fields.name: Auto Finesse Aqua Deluxe Drying Towel
fields.description: The Auto Finesse Aqua Deluxe is the ultimate drying towel. With its large 500mm x 700mm diameter and 1200 g/mÂ² deep pile, it plays a brilliant role in absorbing the entire surface water. It features just the perfect size for reaching the different areas of your vehicle with ease. The Auto Finesse Aqua Deluxe Drying Towel features an ultra-deep, incredibly absorbent 75:25 (polyester:polyamide) weave that performs the ideal drying off and mopping up duties. The tag-free design and soft microfibre edging eliminate the danger of causing any surface marring.

fields.name: Wash Mitt
fields.description: Highly absorbent, the Wash Mitt is easy to use, provides a secure fit and does the job in giving your car a good old wash.

fields.name: Meguiars Super Thick Microfibre Car Wash Mitt
fields.description: Get that showroom finish for your car with the Meguiars Super Thick Microfibre Car Wash Mitt. The microfibre loops lifts dirt and grime easily to prevent you from scratching your car.This super-soft Microfibre Mitt provides a gentle wash action. The high-quality wash mitt provides the ultimate softness and surface protection.The comfort-fit cuff and soft inner lining make this wash mitt a pleasure to use. This super thick mitt can absorb up to ten times its weight in the wash solution, delivering the ultimate finish on all automobile surfaces

fields.name: Meguiar's Supreme Drying Towel
fields.description: The Meguiar's Supreme Drying Towel is a super-soft and ultra-absorbent microfibre towel that makes drying your car a breeze. Soft and kind on your paint work, this microfibre cloth has a thick pile and comes in an extra-large size to give you maximum coverage and absorption power.

fields.name: Meguiars Lambs Wool Wash Mitt
fields.description: The Meguiars Lambs Wool Wash Mitt is perfect for pampering your car and maintaining its finish. It is much less abrasive than a conventional sponge or wash mitt. The reverse side features a special non-abrasive bug remover.

fields.name: Meguiars RG203 5 Gallon Yellow Bucket
fields.description: This heavy duty Meguiars RG203 5 Gallon Yellow Bucket is the perfect accessory for all your car cleaning needs. We recommend that you add your favourite car shampoo to enhance the appearance and protection of your car's paint finish. For a flawless car cleaning experience, finish off with the Meguiars Professional Grit Guard.

fields.name: Meguiars X3003 Professional Grit Guard
fields.description: The Meguiars X3003 Professional Grit Guard is a radial grid that sits at the bottom of the wash bucket. It isolates any grit, dirt and debris from the wash mitt. Besides, it significantly reduces potential swirls and scratches to your vehicle as all of the debris settles to the bottom of the bucket. The wash solution remains cleaner for longer and the paint is protected from swirl-inducing abrasives.

fields.name: Heavy Duty Bucket
fields.description: The Heavy Duty Bucket is made from tough, long-lasting plastic and is ideal for cleaning your car, gardening and general household chores

fields.name: Martin Cox White Valeting Bucket 20L
fields.description: The Martin Cox White Valeting Bucket 20L is a perfect companion to any detailer or valeter, and can be combined with a coordinating grit guard.

fields.name: Turtle Wax Hybrid Hydrophobic Sealant Wax 500ML
fields.description: Turtle Wax Hybrid Sealant Wax contains proprietary Hydrophobic Sealants infused with natural carnauba waxes to create levels of shine and surface slickness never seen before in a spray wax. Stunning results are sealed into the vehicles exterior surfaces ensuring that future washing and drying is even easier. Even though this car wax spray works as a sealant, all types of wax can be applied as an additional layer of shine and protection without diminishing the performance of either.

fields.name: Auto Finesse Lavish Ceramic Snow Foam - 1L
fields.description: Take your protection to new heights with more ease. Lavish Ceramic snow foam is the quick and easy way to apply a layer of ceramic protection to all exterior surfaces of your vehicle, from paintwork to glass, alloy wheels to trim. Simply apply via a foam lance to a clean, wet vehicle for fast even coverage, rinse and dry for shine and protection and water behaviour you can instantly see.

fields.name: Meguiars Gold Class Car Shampoo and Conditioner 1.89 Litre
fields.description: Rich and luxurious, the Meguiar's Gold Class Car Shampoo and Conditioner is designed to both wash and condition in one easy step. The premium formula offers rich suds that gently and safely foams away tough dirt, road grime, and contaminants.

fields.name: Auto Finesse Avalanche Snow Foam 1L
fields.description: The Auto Finesse Avalanche Snow Foam effortlessly removes dirt and road grime from your car's exterior. The thick citrus infused foam cleanses paintwork, removing road contaminants that are picked up from everyday driving. Prepping your vehicle for the contact-wash stage.

fields.description: The Turtle Wax Hybrid Solutions Pro 1 & Done Compound Correct & Finish is the go-to solution for pros and skilled auto enthusiasts that are looking to upgrade their car detailing arsenal.
